SIGNUP

Feature - Signup as a student 

so that I can upload my videos for different categories

Feature - Signup as a judge

so that I can judge videos uploaded by students

Feature - Signup as an admin

using the invite link to view results and manage the system



LOGIN

Feature - authenticate admin

using a password



JUDGE

Feature - Choose choice of judging

either by a category or a user name or all videos


Feature - Give ratings to a video

based on multiple parameters





ADMIN_VIEW

Feature - View top judged videos

of all videos / per parameter


Feature - filter results

based on categories / type of judge



Feature - provide the judge with videos

randomly selected from the lot.


STUDENT


Feature - upload videos

check constraints - one video per category / proper format




